## Architecture

Overlay component at `src/app/components/AppFirewall.tsx`. Default export. Renders floating panels and Leaflet arc layers over the shared WorldMap. Does NOT render its own container or map â€” the Leaflet map is shared with the Privacy Map view via `firewallMode` prop on WorldMap.

