## Layout

Overlay elements positioned over the shared Leaflet WorldMap:

| Element | Position | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| StatusGradient | `absolute top-0`, full width, z-[600] | Same component as Privacy Map, vpnStatus="protected" |
| Left Panel | `absolute top-[8px] left-[8px] bottom-[8px]`, z-[1000], w-[340px] | Glassmorphism panel with app list |
| Right Panel | `absolute top-[8px] right-[8px]`, z-[1000], w-[240px] | Summary stats + review flow |
| Notification Banner | `absolute top-[16px]`, z-[2000] | Centered between panels |
| Bottom Stats Bar | `absolute bottom-0`, z-[1000] | Same gradient pattern as ConnectionDetails |
| Detail Overlay | `absolute inset-0`, z-[3000] | Centered modal with glassmorphism |
| Leaflet Arc Layers | Native Leaflet polylines in L.layerGroup | Auto-handle pan/zoom |

